notes.legend: Dormant volcano. Height: 13022 ft.

notes.name: Nazin Hot Springs
notes.legend: A geothermal springs with naturally heated water that provide relaxation and medicinal benefits. Average temperature is 75°F.

notes.name: Alvesazinde Purifying Well
notes.legend: This legendary water source is whispered about in ancient tales and believed to possess mystical properties. The spring emanates crystal-clear water, shimmering with an otherworldly iridescence that sparkles even in the dimmest light.

notes.legend: Dirdol is a mining town of 786 people just nearby the iron mine.
